{"ec":"ET00013418","t":"Raanjhanaa","img":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/thumbnail/large/raanjhanaa-et00013418-1743768874.jpg","og":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/listing/xxlarge/raanjhanaa-et00013418-1743768874.jpg","d":"Kundan, a Shiv Bhakt-Pandit from Benaras, has a special place in his heart for his childhood love interest, Zoya, a quiet and beautiful girl. Despite her initial dismissal, Kundan`s love for Zoya grows stronger over time. <br/> <br/>When Zoya returns to Benaras, Kundan is excited to tell her about his feelings. However, Zoya is in love with Akram, a college friend from Delhi, and wants Kundan`s help in marrying him. Kundan is torn between his feelings for Zoya and her plea to help her find true love. He sets out to unite her with Akram, a tale of love, betrayal, redemption, and healing set against the rooted town of Benaras and the political landscape of Delhi.","rd":"2013-06-21","rt":146,"ct":"UA","g":["Drama","Romantic"],"l":["Hindi"],"f":["2D"],"i":null,"cast":[["Dhanush","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/dhanush-3988-18-09-2017-03-32-21.jpg"],["Sonam Kapoor Ahuja","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/sonam-kapoor-ahuja-2818-21-05-2018-11-54-38.jpg"],["Abhay Deol","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/abhay-deol-48-13-09-2017-04-01-59.jpg"],["Swara Bhasker","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/swara-bhaskar-18916-12-01-2017-04-40-31.jpg"],["Mohammed Zeeshan Ayyub","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/mohammed-zeeshan-ayyub-27821-24-03-2017-14-10-22.jpg"],["Kumud Mishra","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/kumud-mishra-1238-23-10-2017-03-06-51.jpg"],["Shilpi Marwaha","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/shilpi-marwaha-39125-24-03-2017-16-07-12.jpg"],["Sujata Kumar","h